        SELECT t.Region_Code AS RegionCode, t.Region_Name AS RegionName, t.Country_Code AS CountryCode
        FROM TM_REG_Region AS t
        INNER JOIN TM_COT_Country AS t0 ON t.Country_Code == t0.Country_Code
        WHERE t0.Country_Name == @__countryName_0), 
    Func<QueryContext, DbDataReader, ResultContext, SingleQueryResultCoordinator, TmRegRegion>, 
    Job_Offre.Entities.offres_JobContext, 
    False, 
    False, 
    True
)'
